{lang-eng}Ranunna dinamulalo sthiramuga nunda dayachupumu,
Nannu nike arpinnchukondun,
Nidu mataku lobadedan (nede natho matladumu){/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Maha mahimato vachedavu lokamu ninnu chudajaladhu,
